{"_id":"7AfWj6c77kJwEZxS","name":"In The Mix","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>In The Mix (INT)</p>\n<p>When you concoct a solution on the fly o ut of your alchemical materials, spend one reagent, tell the GM what kind of effect you are trying to produce from up to two kinds of experiments from your Formula Book, and roll+INT.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, choose three.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, choose one.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nothing of value is lost or ruined.</li>\n<li>The effects are confined to their i ntended target.</li>\n<li>There are no unintended side effects.</li>\n<li>The experiment gains or loses the dangerous tag.</li>\n</ul>","choices":"<ul>\n<li>Nothing of value is lost or ruined.</li>\n<li>The effects are confined to their i ntended target.</li>\n<li>There are no unintended side effects.</li>\n<li>The experiment gains or loses the dangerous tag.</li>\n</ul>","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":"<p>On a 7-9, choose one.</p>"},"success":{"value":"<p>On a 10+, choose three.</p>"}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"INT","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7SSd2axOa6TIcyux","name":"Chemistry Wizard","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Chemistry Wizard</p>\n<p>Requires: Mixomancer</p>\n<p>Choose a spell of level 7 or below.</p>\n<p>You add that spell to your formula book as an experiment you can recreate with In The Mix .</p>\n<p>Your GM will tell you what rare reagents you&rsquo;ll need to craft it, and how dangerous it is to do so.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Mixomancer","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
