{"_id":"EXjGNsPnox5fk0lX","name":"Hops, Barley, And Everything Gnarly","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Hops, Barley, And Everything Gnarly</p>\n<p>Add Alcohol experiments to your formula book.</p>\n<p>These experiments are intoxicating.</p>\n<p>When you Carouse with a keg of your homemade ale, you take +1.</p>\n<p>In addition, you&rsquo;ve added your special ingredients - you can mark one reagent to include an experiment from your formula book to the brew.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"LL7fywATPMLBiimN","name":"Formula Book","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Formula Book</p>\n<p>You're a scientist, and you always record your experiments. The result is your formula book, which has what you need to know to recreate those experiments and their effects.</p>\n<p>In addition to healing potion experiments, choose two:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Healing elixirs and salves. These experiments heal [[/r 1d6]] damage</li>\n<li>Explosives: these experiments are explosive, l oud, and d angerous</li>\n<li>Combustibles: these experiments are fiery and dangerous</li>\n<li>Acids and bases: these experiments are d issolving a nd dangerous</li>\n<li>Plant growth: These experiments grow large and entangling plants</li>\n<li>Endotherms: these experiments are f reezing and dangerous</li>\n<li>Electrochemicals: these experiments are e lectric and dangerous</li>\n<li>You can prepare simple mixtures or experiments of these types without a roll at the cost of one alchemical reagent each and a little quiet time.</li>\n</ul>","choices":"","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/sundries/books/book-symbol-triangle-silver-brown.webp","effects":[]}
