{"_id":"Sxc6sPetIPtgJAlI","name":"Homebrewing","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Homebrewing</p>\n<p>When you head to your lab with exotic ingredients ( rare gems, ancient seeds, etc), hoping to brew just the right thing, tell the GM what you're trying to accomplish.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell give you one to four of the following conditions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It's going to take days/weeks/months</li>\n<li>You'll need a test subject, ______ would be perfect</li>\n<li>You'll need a lot of money</li>\n<li>________ has the last ingredient</li>\n<li>The effects will be unstable and temporary</li>\n<li>You'll have to sacrifice the item ________</li>\n<li>It's going to taste very, very bad</li>\n</ul>","choices":"","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"VntC3CRWrsK7ff7V","name":"Polyjuice Potion","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Polyjuice Potion</p>\n<p>Add Transforming e xperiments to your formula book.</p>\n<p>Experiments of this kind transform targets in part or in whole into any animal you have studied closely.</p>\n<p>While transformed, creatures have 1 hold that they may spend to make an animal move.</p>\n<p>When that hold is spent, they revert to their original form.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
