{"_id":"YIZeisgAPV6QbA8G","name":"Magnum Opus","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Magnum Opus</p>\n<p>The first time you h ead to the lab, wielding the alchemical secrets you've discovered after taking this move, you build a prototype of something the world has never seen.</p>\n<p>Tell the GM what your groundbreaking device does and how it works.</p>\n<p>They'll tell you what you need to perfect your invention.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"bU4y0u3ibXpvNl0l","name":"Transmutation","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Transmutation</p>\n<p>You have begun the art of perfecting base metals i nto a purer form.</p>\n<p>When you head to the lab with metal of poor quality, rare resources, and plenty of time, you can transmute those materials i nto Coin or other useful metals.</p>\n<p>The GM will tell you who&rsquo;s interested in acquiring your services.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ibxE1SNfPEQOcTiA","name":"Potionblood","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Potionblood</p>\n<p>Replaces: Internal Alchemy</p>\n<p>You&rsquo;ve consumed a lot of strange liquids in your time, and all that has altered your body chemistry.</p>\n<p>Poisons don&rsquo;t work very well on you, and the bonus and penalty i mposed from Internal Alchemy change to +/-2.</p>\n<p>When you exude strange substances from the liquids you drink, you can inflict the effects of that l iquid on those you touch.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Internal Alchemy","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"me5WH7mpqO1kbQdm","name":"Biovisionary","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Biovisionary</p>\n<p>You&rsquo;ve learned how to bottle some of life&rsquo;s essence. Choose what kind of life you can brew:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Plants</li>\n<li>Animals</li>\n<li>Zombies</li>\n<li>Clones</li>\n</ul>\n<p>When you create life in your lab, roll +INT.</p>\n<p>On a hit, you&rsquo;ve played god and come out on top. Your new being will come to life soon, or maybe in a few weeks.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, everything went according to plan - describe your new being.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, something&rsquo;s not quite right. Share a detail about your creation and the GM will then tell you a detail.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":"<p>On a hit, you&rsquo;ve played god and come out on top. Your new being will come to life soon, or maybe in a few weeks.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, something&rsquo;s not quite right. Share a detail about your creation and the GM will then tell you a detail.</p>"},"success":{"value":"<p>On a hit, you&rsquo;ve played god and come out on top. Your new being will come to life soon, or maybe in a few weeks.</p>\n<p>On a 10+, everything went according to plan - describe your new being.</p>"}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"INT","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nB1M3O4o7dcJ9Q1s","name":"Explosion Elemental","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Explosion Elemental</p>\n<p>Replaces: Volatile Under Pressure</p>\n<p>Your explosive experiments deal [[/r 1d10]] damage and are e xplosive, fiery, dangerous, loud, forceful, and messy.</p>\n<p>In addition, with the right reagents, you can make larger explosives, such as might do serious structural damage to buildings or small towns.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Volatile Under Pressure","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nLFhHNsqyCQaZjar","name":"Gather Reagents","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Gather Reagents</p>\n<p>Almost everything i n the world holds alchemical utility.</p>\n<p>When you spend uninterrupted time scrounging for useful stuff, about an hour or so, you find at l east three uses of alchemical reagents, an abstraction of alchemical items.</p>\n<p>The GM gets final say on if you&rsquo;re in an appropriate place to find things.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Alchemist","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
